PARTICLE LaneGovernanceTopology2026v1
ROLE GOVERNANCE
CATEGORY LANE_TOPOLOGY
VERSIONTAG 2026v1
TITLE Lane governance rules for topology risk r_topology
DESCRIPTION Encodes promotion/downgrade rules based on r_topology SAFE/HARD bands over sliding windows.

FIELDS
policyid            string   LaneGovernanceTopology2026v1
kercontext          string   PhoenixEcoSafetySpine2026v1
planeid             string   topology
corridorid          string   TopologyRiskCorridor2026v1

# Window configuration (number of consecutive windows).
promotion_window_count   i64   # e.g. 4
downgrade_window_count   i64   # e.g. 2

# Band labels must match corridordefinition entries for topology plane.
safe_band_label          string   SAFE
hard_band_label          string   HARD

# Promotion rule: require r_topology <= SAFE band for promotion_window_count windows.
promotion_rule           string   # informal: "rtopology <= SAFE for N windows"

# Downgrade rule: trigger when r_topology >= HARD band for downgrade_window_count windows.
downgrade_rule           string   # informal: "rtopology >= HARD for M windows"

# Evidence and signatures.
evidencehex              string
signingdid               string

END

ROW
policyid=LaneGovernanceTopology2026v1,
kercontext=PhoenixEcoSafetySpine2026v1,
planeid=topology,
corridorid=TopologyRiskCorridor2026v1,
promotion_window_count=4,
downgrade_window_count=2,
safe_band_label=SAFE,
hard_band_label=HARD,
promotion_rule=rtopology<=SAFE for 4 consecutive windows,
downgrade_rule=rtopology>=HARD for 2 consecutive windows,
evidencehex=hex-LaneGovernanceTopology2026v1-proof,
signingdid=bostrom18sd2ujv24ual9c9pshtxys6j8knh6xaead9ye7
END
